 &UR; at play in the media apocalypse, we can seduce the alienated, &LR; 
 &UR; irreverent, unregistered and unbelievable into joining together &LR; 
 &UR; with us, and while they're seduced, we can steal their undies &LR; 
 &UR; and design a new American flag.'' &LR;
