significant amounts of certified organic food, according to Organic
Perspectives magazine.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; By Kim Severson &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; c. 2000 The San Francisco Chronicle &QL;  &LR; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
SAN FRANCISCO _  &UR; WORKING  &LR; _ FAST &AMP; FRESH: Curried Prawns With
