<HEADLINE>
TALENTED ARTISTS, UGLY BELIEFS
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 By DAVE FERMAN 
 c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   When I have to get myself up and going in the morning, I might
listen to Roxy Music, Django Reinhardt, the Tractors, Graham
Parker, Monster Magnet or any number of others.
