<P>
   MIDEAST-SUMMIT _ THURMONT, Md. _ Spot coverage of the final
status peace talks between Israel and the Palestinians. The talks
are expected to wrapup Wednesday and are focused on three issues:
the future of Jerusalem; borders of a Palestinian state; and fate
of millions of Palestinian refugees around the world. Developing.
(Deans, Cox News Service) 30.
</P>
