<P>
   CLINTON-OKINAWA _ NAHA, Okinawa _ As President Clinton arrives
here for a three-day Group of Seven industrial nations (plus
Russia) meeting, he will be greeted by a populace still smoldering
over the presence of U.S. military bases here. We profile this
island in advance of the summit. Developing. (Chao, Cox News
Service) WITH PHOTO and locator map information attached.
</P>
<P>
   EDs: Moving by 1 p.m. (EDT) on the NYT wire in (i) International
and (w) Washington categories.
