<P>
   RUSSIA-OLIGARCHS _ MOSCOW _ The State Duma, Russia lower house
of Parliament, is expected to vote on a proposed law _ backed by
President Vladimir Putin _ that seeks to bring the country's
powerful ``oligarchy'' under more control. It is the first major
salvo to be fired by Putin against Russia's influential business
elite. Developing. (Coker, Cox News Service) 15.
</P>
