``stained-glass ceiling'' that kept women out of the Episcopacy of
the African Methodist Episcopal Church, Bishop Vashti Murphy
McKenzie returns to Ohio Tuesday to deliver the keynote speech at
the Third Episcopal District Christian Education Congress 2000 at
Wilberforce University. (Dayton Daily News) MOVED.
