</P>
<P>
   MIDEAST-SUMMIT (Thurmont, Md.) _ Rumors swirl repeatedly, and
are just as often denied, that Ehud Barak is about to pull out of
President Clinton's Mideast peace talks. By Anne E. Kornblut and
Charles M. Sennott.
</P>
<P>
