   _ ``The West Wing'' is adding a pair of Republicans ( &UR; Peggy &LR; 
 &UR; Noonan  &LR; and  &UR; Marlin Fitzwater &LR; ) to its list of Democratic
consultants ( &UR; Dee Dee Myers &LR; ,  &UR; Patrick Caddell &LR;  and  &UR; Lawrence &LR; 
 &UR; O'Donnell &LR; ), says the Washington Post.
</P>
