<P>
   TELEKOM-VOICESTREAM (Undated) _ In a move that advances the
ambitions of Europe's largest telephone company in the United
States, Deutsche Telekom has offered to acquire VoiceStream
Wireless in a deal that values the American company at about $53
billion, according to a person close to bid. By Simon Romero.
</P>
