<DOCNO> NYT20000719.0486 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-19 23:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7358 &Cx1f; tad-z
b w BC-MIDEAST-SUMMIT-0720-1     07-19 0762
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MIDEAST-SUMMIT-0720-1STLD-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDs: writes thru to update with collapse of talks
